snippet.title: Hunter's Acoustic Cabin
snippet.description:
This is my new channel started during the quarantine of 2020.  I normally live in Los Angeles when not on tour with my band Hunter and the Dirty Jacks, although at the time of this description I am quarantined with my cat Wolfgang in total seclusion in Big Bear Lake, California.

My favorite description of my music is Blues/Rock and I love blues, rock, soul, old country, and just about everything in between that relies on real people playing instruments and voices.  Most of the time that I pick up an instrument it does not require electricity to play (although I'm passionate about amplified Blues Harp on stage), so I do a lot of writing out in nature or beside a fire. A lot of my lyrics tend to reference history, math, science, philosophy and romance. 

 I am probably a complicated man, but trying to lead a simple life.
